Reinforcement Learning. 

Explanation: The paper explicitly mentions the application of reinforcement learning to the problem of elevator dispatching. The challenges posed by the elevator domain, such as continuous state spaces, nonstationarity, and incomplete observation of the state, are all addressed using RL techniques. The results of the simulation demonstrate the effectiveness of RL in solving this practical optimization problem. None of the other sub-categories of AI are mentioned or implied in the text.
